個工作天先加到,中銀係用手機即時加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n即時加都未構成問題,因為仲有預設轉帳限額<br />\n金錢損失理應唔會多過轉帳限額<br />\n但係,中銀個app竟然係話你轉帳限額唔夠果頁,走去問你係咪要提升轉帳限額<br />\n如果㩒左Yes,可以直接提升到銀行存款總額,即時轉走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以,只要有個賊,拎把刀仔指住你條頸要你轉錢去佢account<br />\n你就只能夠將成副身家交俾個賊,再事後報警<br />\n<br />\n老老柒柒,今時今日仲係好多人覺得借個銀行account俾人無乜問題<br />\n得個銀行account真係唔知搵唔搵到個賊<br />\n更何況,錢過到賊手,等到警察查到,個賊都唔知仲係唔係香港啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5693aea317c5fc881328718ba8b40e1bb8e3882","tid":1033724,"uid":99420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"53e4d0637bfda703f5845785ec13803e13d774a3","tid":1033724,"uid":171446,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:39:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b5fa3e88585d5a9798381e45ccba237cb182020","tid":1033724,"uid":70085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67a9db0ea8b4864bbfd094d653df1c84efec95c4","tid":1033724,"uid":182067,"like":1,"dislike":25,"score":-24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-23T11:51:18.000Z","msg":"最新消息：本來中午開唔到app, 而家開到，又login 到，今面好似又唔見有咩異常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家問題就係三個email ，內面又無hyperlink, 電話又係中銀個電話，its_boc@bochk.com send 出黎，究竟咩事呀？<br />\n<br />\n個CS而家成個鐘都冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:42:02.000Z","msg":"個email 應該假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669f795653158c46399ac8bf7d383f3d5deedec5","tid":1033724,"uid":163340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53e4d0637bfda703f5845785ec13803e13d774a3","tid":1033724,"uid":171446,"like":4,"dislike":1,"sco